OL,3,CJanuary sales bargain hunters warned
OL,4,Cof sharp rise in rogue retailers
OL,6,FJanuary sales bargain hunters are
OL,7,Fbeing warned by a bank to watch out
OL,8,Ffor rogue retailers claiming to offer
OL,9,Fbig discounts.
OL,11,FThe number of rogue retailers
OL,12,Fidentified by Lloyds Banking Group in
OL,13,FJanuary 2024 was 140% higher than the
OL,14,Fnormal monthly average across the
OL,15,Fyear, indicating that retailers
OL,16,Ftargeted shoppers looking for deals
OL,17,Fduring the post-Christmas sales.
