OL,3,CJanuary sales bargain hunters warned
OL,4,Cof sharp rise in rogue retailers
OL,6,FRogue retailers deceive shoppers into
OL,7,Fmaking purchases by creating fake
OL,8,Fwebsites, made to look like popular
OL,9,Fhigh-street brands.
OL,11,FBut after shoppers have made the
OL,12,Fpurchase, the scammer pockets the cash
OL,13,Fwithout sending the item.
OL,15,FThe scam can cause credit card
OL,16,Ftransaction disputes to peak in
OL,17,FJanuary, with Lloyds seeing a 40%
OL,18,Fincrease in disputes in January 2024,
OL,19,Fcompared to the normal monthly average.
