OL,3,CJanuary sales bargain hunters warned
OL,4,Cof sharp rise in rogue retailers
OL,6,FLloyds said rogue retailer scams have
OL,7,Fcost #8.5 million between January and
OL,8,FNovember 2024, based on the group's
OL,9,Fown credit and debit card customer
OL,10,Fdata.
OL,12,FThe bank has established an industry
OL,13,Fworking group, working with payments
OL,14,Fcompanies to protect shoppers by
OL,15,Freporting and blocking transactions
OL,16,Fwith known fake websites.
