OL,3,CJanuary sales bargain hunters warned
OL,4,Cof sharp rise in rogue retailers
OL,6,FGavin Evans, senior manager for
OL,7,Fconsumer cards at Lloyds, said: "The
OL,8,FJanuary sales can be a good time to
OL,9,Fgrab bargains, but it's also a popular
OL,10,Ftime for rogue retailers, who try to
OL,11,Fscam unsuspecting shoppers and pocket
OL,12,Ftheir hard-earned cash.
OL,14,F"To avoid being caught out, check the
OL,15,Fweb address before making a purchase
OL,16,Fto ensure that it is legitimate and
OL,17,Fmatches the shop you're looking to buy
OL,18,Ffrom, especially if you opened the
OL,19,Fwebsite by clicking on an advert or
OL,20,Fsocial media post.
