OL,3,CJanuary sales bargain hunters warned
OL,4,Cof sharp rise in rogue retailers
OL,6,F"Remember that if something appears
OL,7,Ftoo good to be true, it usually is. If
OL,8,Fyou're ever unsure, consider buying
OL,9,Ffrom somewhere you trust instead."
OL,11,FHere are some tips from Mr Evans to
OL,12,Favoid losing money:
OL,14,F1. Firstly, try contacting the
OL,15,Fretailer directly to explain what has
OL,16,Fhappened and request a refund.
