OL,3,CJanuary sales bargain hunters warned
OL,4,Cof sharp rise in rogue retailers
OL,6,F2. If the retailer does not respond or
OL,7,Frefuses to refund you, report the
OL,8,Ftransaction to your bank. Many will
OL,9,Fallow you to report transactions
OL,10,Fonline in your mobile banking app.
OL,12,F3. If you have paid by card, you could
OL,13,Fask your bank to file a chargeback
OL,14,Fclaim. You will need to give your bank
OL,15,Fthe details of the transaction you are
OL,16,Fdisputing and a description of what
OL,17,Fwent wrong with the item you ordered.
