OL,3,CJanuary sales bargain hunters warned
OL,4,Cof sharp rise in rogue retailers
OL,6,F4. If you made the purchase using your
OL,7,Fcredit card, you may be able to make a
OL,8,Fclaim under Section 75 of the Consumer
OL,9,FCredit Act. Your bank will be able to
OL,10,Fguide you through what you need to do.
OL,12,FIn addition to Mr Evans's tips, new
OL,13,Frules came into force last autumn
OL,14,Frequiring banks to reimburse people
OL,15,Fwho are tricked into transferring
OL,16,Fmoney directly to a fraudster. The
OL,17,Fauthorised push payment (APP) scam
OL,18,Frules are overseen by the Payment
OL,19,FSystems Regulator (PSR).
